# API Configuration
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api

# Razorpay Configuration
VITE_RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=rzp_test_your_key_id_here

# CloudFront Configuration
VITE_CLOUDFRONT_URL=https://your-cloudfront-domain.cloudfront.net

# Notes:
# 1. All Vite environment variables must start with VITE_ prefix
# 2. Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual values
# 3. Never commit .env file to version control
# 4. For production deployment:
#    - Set VITE_API_URL to your Vercel backend URL
#    - Use rzp_live_ prefix for production Razorpay keys
# 5. These variables are exposed to the browser, so don't store secrets here